div.div:
Class Stereotype Notes
The dark grey class, the MOBLIMA class, is the Boundary Object as it is the point of interaction for users with the whole app.
The light grey classes, the Module and DB classes, are the Control objects the mediate interactions and the flow of data between the MOBLIMA Boundary and the Entities
The white classes, the Object classes, are the Entity objects that contain the underlying data needed for the app to function.
